'''HP Quality Center'''（意为“惠普质量中心”）是{{tsl|en|HP Software Division|惠普软件事业部}}的一款品质管理软件。其多数功能是从收购{{tsl|en|Mercury Interactive}}公司而来的<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.hp.com/hpinfo/newsroom/press/2006/061107xa.html |title=HP Closes Landmark Mercury Acquisition; Companies Unite to Lead in Business Technology Optimization Software |publisher=Hewlett Packard |date=2006-11-07 |accessdate=2013-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202041615/http://www.hp.com/hpinfo/newsroom/press/2006/061107xa.html |archivedate=2013-02-02 }}</ref>。HP Quality Center提供[[软件质量保证|SQA]]，包括针对[[IT|IT]]和应用程序的[[需求管理|需求管理]]、{{tsl|en|test management|测试管理}}和[[业务过程|业务过程]]测试<ref>{{cite web |url=https://h10078.www1.hp.com/cda/hpms/display/main/hpms_content.jsp?zn=bto&cp=1-11-127_4000_100__ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-07-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091223111403/https://h10078.www1.hp.com/cda/hpms/display/main/hpms_content.jsp?zn=bto&cp=1-11-127_4000_100__ |archivedate=2009-12-23 }}</ref>。HP Quality Center是{{tsl|en|HP Application Lifecycle Management|惠普应用程序生命周期管理}}软件解决方案集的一个组成部分<ref>{{cite web |last=Jackson |first=Joab |url=http://www.cio.com/article/641167/HP_Fuses_Dev_Management_and_Testing_Tools |title=HP Fuses Dev Management and Testing Tools |publisher=CIO.com |date=2010-11-30 |accessdate=2013-02-11 |archive-date=2012-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008044954/http://www.cio.com/article/641167/HP_Fuses_Dev_Management_and_Testing_Tools |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 产品形式 ==
HP Quality Center有HP Quality Center入门版和HP Quality Center企业版软件可用。入门版针对入门级的软件质量保证组织；企业版原名Mercury TestDirector，适用于管理大中型软件的软件质量保证组织。HP Quality Center也可以[[软件即服务|软件即服务]]形式使用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eoh-am.co.za/live/content.php?Item_ID=2671 |title=HP Quality Center in the Cloud |publisher=Eoh-am.co.za |date= |accessdate=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2014-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303203220/http://www.eoh-am.co.za/live/content.php?Item_ID=2671 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

